    封闭类:
    OutputLogger

    public static class OutputLogger.OutputPrintStream
extends PrintStream
    A print stream class to capture all data from stdout and stderr.
    版本:
    $Revision: 4716 $
    作者:
    fracpete (fracpete at waikato dot ac dot nz)
